<div class="postright">
<h3>Re: AMD drivers</h3>
<div class="postmsg">
<p>fglrx is not well maintained by AMD/ATI.. it needs an old xorg server that is not present anymore in Debian 9, so you want be able to use it on Parrot 3.7. <br/>You will need to wait and see if AMD decides to update that driver.</p>
</div>
